This reads CloudWatch Logs directly.

âŒ Errors Faced & How We Fixed Them (INTERVIEW GOLD)
âŒ Error 1: AWS credentials missing

Cause: AWS CLI not configured
âœ… Fix:

aws configure

âŒ Error 2: nodejs14.x is no longer supported

Cause: Old Lambda runtime
âœ… Fix:

runtime: nodejs18.x

âŒ Error 3: Cannot find module 'uuid'

Cause: Dependency not packaged
âœ… Fix:

npm install uuid
serverless deploy

âŒ Error 4: Internal Server Error

Cause: Lambda crash (check logs)
âœ… Fix:

serverless logs -f kaamBharo

